title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Missile Lock-On Jammers
content:
The Missile Lock-On Jammer mod is available for purchase at an Agency Vehicle Workshop. With this upgrade, players won’t be able to lock on to your vehicles whenever they fancy blowing them up.

Head on down to your Agency Vehicle Workshop to apply the Missile Lock-On Jammer to a growing list of eligible vehicles.

GTA+ Members have the extra benefit of accessing this mod at The Vinewood Club Garage’s Vehicle Workshop
